# Rule 02 - Enterprise Domain Driven Design v2
# Part 1 - Strategic Domain Design

# Purpose

Domain Driven Design is the foundation of the AI Sales Employee Platform.

Every feature starts with the business domain.

Never start with

Database

↓

API

↓

Entity

↓

Controller

Always start with

Business Problem

↓

Business Capability

↓

Domain

↓

Bounded Context

↓

Aggregate

↓

Implementation

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

# DDD Philosophy

The software model must represent the business.

Business language drives

Architecture

Database

APIs

Events

AI

Workflow

Plugins

Never allow technical implementation to define the domain.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Ubiquitous Language

Every bounded context owns its own language.

Examples

Lead Context

